<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Crew" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Crew,</orth> company, band: <cit><quote>Collatine and all his lordly c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1731" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1731</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>we'll bring thee to our --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.1.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. IV, 1, 74</bibl></cit>(?). <cit><quote>a c. of patches,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so dissolute a c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that consorted c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 12</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>art thou of Cornish c.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.50" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 50</bibl></cit> (Pistol's speech). <cit><quote>all the c. of them,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.72" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 72</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to London all the c. are gone,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.174" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 174</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with a valiant c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.5.12" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 5, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a c. of wretched souls,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 141</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a c. of pirates,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 5.1.176" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 1, 176</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>